ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v251.message

Class OUL_R22

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v251.message.OUL_R22
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class OUL_R22
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a OUL_R22 message structure (see chapter 7.3.7). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional
    • 4: OUL_R22_PATIENT (a Group object) optional
    • 5: OUL_R22_VISIT (a Group object) optional
    • 6: OUL_R22_SPECIMEN (a Group object) repeating
    • 7: DSC (Continuation Pointer) optional
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
